00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:30,390
Oh, my God!

46
00:02:30,390 --> 00:02:31,390
They’re smiling.

47
00:02:31,390 --> 00:02:35,519
Suddenly, they gain lots of attention, all these positive reinforcements, so they do

