can’t hear or see the feedback, also smile at about the same time as children who are

52
00:02:50,190 --> 00:02:51,270
not deaf or blind.

53
00:02:51,270 --> 00:02:55,299
That, again, suggests an evolutionary function.

54
00:02:55,299 --> 00:02:59,260
We spoke about the fact that some of these emotions are seen across species, particularly

55
